									<children>
										<node id="data" key="key">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player, being physically in the Astral plane, enters a full-blown battle. Before us, 4 of Orpheus' guards fight against a mind flayer, The Emperor/Daisy.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The Emperor holds his hands up, they are buzzing with psionic energy. He is trying to recreate the globe of domination with one hand, and uses telekenis with the other to fling a stone toward the guards.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;One of the guards kicks the stone to the side, following through to knock the Emperor down toward the player." />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
