											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="In the absence of the globe of domination we see the chains that bind Orpheus stop glowing. Orpheus’ head straightens to its natural position as he ‘awakens’. A closeup on Orpheus’ face as his eyes roll back to their natural state. He is ‘free’ of the Emperor’s psionic control (though still unable to move.)" />
