											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The globe stops forming.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;At the centre, Orpheus is chained (with VFX lightning chains) to a rock by the infernal shackles he wears, unmoving, his eyes rolled back to the whites (or equivalent cool VFX suggesting he is subdued.) His head is also snapped back so that he looks unseeing at the sky. " />
